到深水灣、淺水灣、赤柱<br />\n3. MTR <br />\n4. 附近巴士站<br />\n5. 走返去香港仔、華富（域多利道）"},{"pid":"965c4f694ff1f7579f8ac8a9c8c4cd9ff7c78d80","tid":1381644,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:21:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cacbfdf4bbbda5bbfae64ce443c8ed2490b4b4f","tid":1381644,"uid":246118,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:25:42.000Z","msg":"南區太危險，交通唔方便"},{"pid":"aa8afffe2c4221da4412958f14356398dd836514","tid":1381644,"uid":11937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:26:14.000Z","msg":"互相推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「全港大罷工」動搖唔到經濟民生佔晒全香港都無用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380596\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380596</a>"},{"pid":"f327dc6bfbe24404d45e9a6fa6635a56c6efff63","tid":1381644,"uid":9707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"南區最多搞光復田灣<br />\n但退路唔係有好多<br />\n地鐵，只要金鐘站暫停成條鐵就廢左<br />\n香港仔時光隧道，塞車或者封路就走唔到<br />\n薄扶林道set RB巴士同校巴服務點都會有影響<br />\n入赤柱或者行黃泥涌道走又冇乜交通工具<br />\n只要班狗守死呢幾條路，基本上散唔到<br />\n唔通去香港仔水塘行山落灣仔或者搭大飛走？"},{"pid":"7e89b21227225c29e3537fcdef3d23885825ba4e","tid":1381644,"uid":109090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:44:32.000Z","msg":"唔可以搞黃竹坑站，成個南區得兩條路，放工時間會倒灌番銅鑼灣"},{"pid":"6f8aae9a16c2d698fe0432fa6148a3b3486c158c","tid":1381644,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實南區真係好和平<br />\n<br />\n利申 華貴"},{"pid":"8069274f8247ed5f27e5b08cc14a857973eefabf","tid":1381644,"uid":74128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f8aae9a16c2d698fe0432fa6148a3b3486c158c","tid":1381644,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm